  56:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****               The static linked-list format refers to the full linked-list node where all DMA chann
  57:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****               fetched and executed independently of the redundancy of information.
