  61:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****               parameters are fetched and executed (Example: data size = 20 on previous node, and da
  62:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****               current node => No need to update it).
